rums, tapping out rhythms on the bongos, creating melodies on a keyboard, or shaking maracas to the beat, *Drum Circle* brings the joy of music-making to life in immersive VR.\n\n**Features:**\n- Play a range of instruments: congas, bongos, keyboards, and maracas!\n- Play along with *music tracks* or create your own rhythms and melodies\n- Intuitive hand-tracking lets you perform naturally without controllers.\n\nGet ready to feel the rhythm, unleash your creativity, and make music like never before with *Drum Circle*!", "short_description": "Unleash your inner musician with Drum Circle! Step into a vibrant virtual world where you can play a variety of instruments using just your hands. Whether you're grooving on the conga drums, tapping out rhythms on the bongos, creating melodies on a keyboard, or shaking maracas to the beat, Drum Circle brings the joy of music-making to life in immersive VR."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://artisanreality.com/privacy-policy-for-drum-circle", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Artisan Effects", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://artisanreality.com/drum-circle", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "331529188132278"}, {"id": "1672577396871977"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH", "HAND_TRACKING"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "9275428802471697"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 3, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED"